4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SecurityConfigurer</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Http요청과 관련된 보안 처리를 담당하는 필터들을 생성하고 인증 및 인가 초기화 작업</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"securitybuilder\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#securitybuilder\" aria-label=\"securitybuilder permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SecurityBuilder</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>빌더 클래스로 웹 보안을 구성하는 빈 객체와 설정클래스 생성 ex) WebSeucrity, HttpSecurity</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"securityBuilder.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>AutoConfiguration이 SecurityBuilder를 생성하면 SecurityConfigurer를 초기화 (init, configure)</li>\n<li>WebSecurity, HttpSecurity 순을 객체 생성</li>\n<li>SecurityFilterChain이름을 가진 FilterChainProxy생성</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"초기화-과정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B4%88%EA%B8%B0%ED%99%94-%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"초기화 과정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>초기화 과정</h2>\n<h2 id=\"authenticationentirypoint\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#authenticationentirypoint\" aria-label=\"authenticationentirypoint permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>AuthenticationEntiryPoint</h2>\n<h2 id=\"인증-인가-흐름\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EC%A6%9D-%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%80-%ED%9D%90%EB%A6%84\" aria-label=\"인증 인가 흐름 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인증, 인가 흐름</h2>\n<h2 id=\"cors\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cors\" aria-label=\"cors permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cors</h2>\n<h1 id=\"oauth20\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#oauth20\" aria-label=\"oauth20 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>OAuth2.0</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>자신이 소유한 리소스에 소프트웨어 애플리케이션이 접근할 수 있도록 허용해 줌으로써 접근 권한을 위임해주는 개방형 표준 프로토콜</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"주요-용어\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%EC%9A%A9%EC%96%B4\" aria-label=\"주요 용어 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주요 용어</h2>\n<p>Authentication(인증)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>접근 자격이 있는지 검증</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Authorization(인가)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>자원에 접근할 권한 부여</li>\n<li>인가가 완료되면 리소스 접근 권한이 담긴 Access Token이 클라이언트에게 부여</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Access Token</p>\n<ul>\n<li>리소스 서버에 접근 시 사용되는 만료 기간이 있는 Token</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Refresh Token</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Access Token 만료시 이를 갱신하기 위한 용도로 사용하는 Token</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"oauth-20-role\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#oauth-20-role\" aria-label=\"oauth 20 role permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>OAuth 2.0 Role</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>OAuth 2.0의 매커니즘은 다음 네가지 종류의 역할을 담당하는 주체에 의해 이루어지는 권한 부여 체계</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"resource-owner-자원-소유자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#resource-owner-%EC%9E%90%EC%9B%90-%EC%86%8C%EC%9C%A0%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"resource owner 자원 소유자 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Resource Owner (자원 소유자)</h2>\n<h2 id=\"resource-server-보호자원-서버\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#resource-server-%EB%B3%B4%ED%98%B8%EC%9E%90%EC%9B%90-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84\" aria-label=\"resource server 보호자원 서버 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Resource Server (보호자원 서버)</h2>\n<h2 id=\"authorization-server-인가-서버\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#authorization-server-%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%80-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84\" aria-label=\"authorization server 인가 서버 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Authorization Server (인가 서버)</h2>\n<h2 id=\"clinet\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#clinet\" aria-label=\"clinet permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Clinet</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>qh</li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"Security Fundamentals SecurityBuilder, SecurityConfigurer SecurityConfigurer Http요청과 관련된 보안 처리를 담당하는 필터들을 생성하고 인증 및 인가 초기화 작업 SecurityBuild…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/SpringSecurity2/#security-fundamentals\">Security Fundamentals</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/SpringSecurity2/#securitybuilder-securityconfigurer\">SecurityBuilder, SecurityConfigurer</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/SpringSecurity2/#securityconfigurer\">SecurityConfigurer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/SpringSecurity2/#securitybuilder\">SecurityBuilder</a></li